lead_paragraph: Poels attacked near the end and held off the Swiss veteran Michael Albasini to take the 154-mile Liege-Bastogne-Liege classic in Belgium, the biggest win of his career.

headline.main: Dutch Rider Wout Poels Prevails in Belgium

snippet: Poels attacked near the end and held off the Swiss veteran Michael Albasini to take the 154-mile Liege-Bastogne-Liege classic in Belgium, the biggest win of his career.
abstract: Dutch rider Wout Poels wins Liege-Bastogne-Liege classic in Belgium.
